       true,
       "functools.partialmethod.__get__.__qualname__.__eq__('partialmethod.__get__') == True — partialmethod defines a __get__ method to act as a descriptor; when accessed from an instance it returns a bound partial; its __qualname__ is 'partialmethod.__get__'; str.__eq__('partialmethod.__get__') returns True; new to extra162"]
