       true,
       "functools.partialmethod.__module__.__class__.__name__.__eq__('str') == True — __module__ is a Python str recording the module where the class is defined; for partialmethod it is 'functools'; __class__.__name__ is 'str'; str.__eq__('str') returns True; new to extra162"]

